  "body": "Matches six functions and improves several remaining partial matches across cm, ft, gm, gr, if, mn, and ty.\n\nMatches:\n- `Camera_80030E44`\n- `ftAction_80073008`\n- `fn_8017A9B4`\n- `un_80318B1C`\n- `ftNn_Init_80123954`\n- `gm_801A9DD0`\n\nAdditional improvements:\n- `mn_8022FB88`\n- `grInishie2_801FD9EC`\n- `un_803147C4`\n- `un_80303FD4`\n- `un_802FF570`\n- `gmCamera_801A292C`\n- `ftKb_SpecialN_800EED50`\n- `fn_802FA6C4`\n- `ft_800852B0`\n- `fn_80175A94`\n\nVerification:\n- `python configure.py --require-protos`\n- `ninja`\n- GALE01 report shows the six listed matches at 100.0%, with the listed partial functions improved from upstream.",
